HEADWORD: Ceraunoscope
<hw>Ce*rau"no*scope</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
thunder and lightning + <ets>-scope</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument or
apparatus employed in the ancient mysteries to imitate thunder and
lightning.</def> <rj><au>T. Moore.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
